fields.label: Clear Marine Snaps
fields.content: CLEAR Adhesive Marine Snaps - $15 for a set of 5. These little neoprene doo-dads are pricey but very useful! They work for surfaces you don’t want to (or can’t) screw into, including tile, concrete, smooth brick, metal, and vinyl surfaces. They are not suitable for rough surfaces like stucco, HardiPlank®, or sandstone.
